title: Catalan parliament declares independence
description:
► Subscribe to FT.com here: http://bit.ly/2r8RJzM

Catalonia’s parliament has voted overwhelmingly in favour of independence from Spain even as the Spanish authorities moved to take direct control of the powerful and wealthy region.
